title: Homemade Pork Croquettes & Gravy Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! With a crunchy, golden exterior and a savoury, meaty centre, every bite of these croquetas will
transport you to a bustling tapas bar right in the heart of Spain. Let’s add a creamy mash that packs a punch with Dijon mustard
and an easy gravy to pour all over.
